      • idEquals

        protected final <T extends Entity<ID>> T idEquals(Class<? extends T> type,
                                                  Object obj)
        Checks if an object is an instance of an entity type and its id is equals to this entity id.
        Parameters:
        type - Entity type.
        obj - Object to check.
        Returns:
        The object casts to type if the object is an instance of type and the object and this entity have the same id (even if the id is null). Null otherwise.

      • idHashCode

        protected final int idHashCode()
        Returns the hash code of the id of the entity. If the id is null a constant number is returned.
